  "title": "Gemini 和 Whisk 迎来 Veo 2：视频创作新纪元",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/generate-videos-in-gemini-and-whisk-with-veo-2/",
  "date": "2025-04-16 00:37:01",
  "author": "Angela Sun",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-04-16T00:37:01.268769+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$65960231014$--><span width=\"14px\">\n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg></span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable> <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"hzfux\" class=\"drop-cap\">Starting today, Gemini Advanced users can generate and share videos using our state-of-the-art video model, <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/video-image-generation-update-december-2024/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/video-image-generation-update-december-2024/&quot;}\">Veo 2</a>. In Gemini, you can now translate text-based prompts into dynamic videos. Google Labs is also making Veo 2 available through <a href=\"http://labs.google/whisk\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://labs.google/whisk&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Whisk</a>, a generative AI experiment that allows you to create new images using both text and image prompts, and now animate them into videos.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"6uggf\">How to create videos with Gemini</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"emffm\">Veo 2 represents a <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/veo/veo-2/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/veo/veo-2/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">leap forward</a> in video generation, designed to produce high-resolution, detailed videos with cinematic realism. By better understanding real-world physics and human motion, it delivers fluid character movement, lifelike scenes and finer visual details across diverse subjects and styles.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4v3c0\">To generate videos, select Veo 2 from the model dropdown <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-1\" id=\"footnote-source-1\"><sup>1</sup></a> in Gemini. This feature creates an eight-second video clip at 720p resolution, delivered as an MP4 file in a 16:9 landscape format. There is a monthly limit on how many videos you can create, but we will notify you as you approach it.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"ebedu\"><a href=\"https://gemini.google/overview/video-generation/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://gemini.google/overview/video-generation/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Creating videos</a> with Gemini is simple: just describe the scene you want to create — whether it's a short story, a visual concept, or a specific scene — and Gemini will bring your ideas to life. The more detailed your description, the more control you have over the final video. This opens up a world of fun creative possibilities, letting your imagination go wild to picture unreal combinations, explore varied visual styles from realism to fantasy, or quickly narrate short visual ideas.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"c6t8m\">One of the best parts of creating is sharing with others. Sharing your video on mobile is easy: simply tap the share button to quickly upload engaging short videos to platforms like TikTok and YouTube Shorts.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-image-carousel section-header=\"Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Generated_Video__37_aDEwjss.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Animation of two figures in white exosuits casting light in a cave&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Gemini 1&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Mouse_Reads_Video_Generated.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Animation of an adorable mouse reading a book&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;Gemini 2&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Generated_Video__13.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Animation of cliffs on a beach&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;pacific view&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot; https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/KR_Veo2_4.mp4 &quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Animation of pixelated ice cream melting&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;KR_Veo2_4.mp4&quot;\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Article Carousel&quot;, &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2&quot;}\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n     <button class=\"article-carousel__arrow article-carousel__arrow--previous\" data-ga4-analytics-carousel-scroll-click=\"{&quot;toggle_type_direction&quot;: &quot;arrow - left&quot;}\" aria-label=\"Previous\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067\"><uni-icon-component iconid=\"mi-keyboard-arrow-right\">\n       <!---->\n       <svg class=\"icon \" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\">\n        <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250415-2003#mi-keyboard-arrow-right\"></use>\n       </svg>\n      </uni-icon-component></button>\n     <button class=\"article-carousel__arrow article-carousel__arrow--next\" data-ga4-analytics-carousel-scroll-click=\"{&quot;toggle_type_direction&quot;: &quot;arrow - right&quot;}\" aria-label=\"Next\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067\"><uni-icon-component iconid=\"mi-keyboard-arrow-right\">\n       <!---->\n       <svg class=\"icon \" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\">\n        <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250415-2003#mi-keyboard-arrow-right\"></use>\n       </svg>\n      </uni-icon-component></button>\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1744797905067\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 411.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$65960231014$--><!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1744797905067-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 4\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n         <div class=\"article-carousel__slide-img article-carousel__video-slide\">\n          <video autoplay=\"\" class=\"article-carousel__media\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Animation of two figures in white exosuits casting light in a cave\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Generated_Video__37_aDEwjss.mp4\">\n           Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Generated_Video__37_aDEwjss.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a>and watch it with your favorite video player!\n          </video>\n         </div>\n        </div><!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"27cbd\">Prompt: A wide, slow-panning shot of an enormous glacial cavern, bathed in eerie twilight. Pale cyan light filters from above, illuminating frozen candy figures within the ice walls. Two figures in white exosuits, their helmet lights casting beams, trudge through the center. Capture the cavern's scale and stillness.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!---->\n     </div><!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$65960231014$--><!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067-0\"><!--?lit$65960231014$-->1</button><!----><!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067-1\"><!--?lit$65960231014$-->2</button><!----><!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067-2\"><!--?lit$65960231014$-->3</button><!----><!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1744797905067-3\"><!--?lit$65960231014$-->4</button><!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"be4dh\">Video generation is now rolling out to Gemini Advanced users globally on web and mobile, starting today and continuing over the next few weeks. This feature is available to Google One AI Premium subscribers in all languages Gemini supports. Try it out today at <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://gemini.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gemini.google.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"be4dh\">How Whisk Animate brings your images to life</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"qrhp\"><a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/whisk/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/whisk/&quot;}\">Introduced in December</a>, Whisk is a Google Labs experiment that helps you quickly explore and visualize new ideas using both text and image prompts. Today, you can animate your creations with Whisk Animate.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2bhtn\">Whisk Animate lets you turn your images into vivid eight-second videos using Veo 2. It’s available for Google One AI Premium subscribers globally starting today. Subscribers can try it at <a href=\"http://labs.google/whisk\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://labs.google/whisk&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">labs.google/whisk</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-youtube-player-article index=\"5\" thumbnail-alt=\"Video of Whisk Animate\" video-id=\"2yYDI-p5aGs\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Youtube Video&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"2yYDI-p5aGs\" data-index-id=\"5\" data-type=\"video\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n      <a role=\"video\" class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/2yYDI-p5aGs/default.webp\" alt=\"Video of Whisk Animate\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/2yYDI-p5aGs/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/2yYDI-p5aGs/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250415-2003#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250415-2003#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><!--?lit$65960231014$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component iconid=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250415-2003#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Generate videos in Gemini and Whisk with Veo 2&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"be4dh\">How we approach safety</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"94fmg\">We’ve taken important steps to make video generation a safe experience. This includes extensive <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/safety-security/googles-ai-red-team-the-ethical-hackers-making-ai-safer/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/safety-security/googles-ai-red-team-the-ethical-hackers-making-ai-safer/&quot;}\">red teaming</a> and evaluation aimed at preventing the generation of content that violates our <a href=\"https://gemini.google/policy-guidelines/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://gemini.google/policy-guidelines/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">policies</a>. Additionally, all videos generated with Veo 2 are marked with <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/synthid/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/technologies/synthid/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SynthID</a>, a digital watermark embedded in each frame, which indicates the videos are AI-generated.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"a9rsg\">Gemini's outputs are primarily determined by user prompts and like any generative AI tool, there may be instances where it generates content that some individuals find objectionable. We’ll continue to listen to your feedback through the thumbs up/down buttons and make ongoing improvements. For more details, you can <a href=\"https://gemini.google/our-approach/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://gemini.google/our-approach/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">read about our approach on our website</a>.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2dv5b\">We hope you enjoy making videos in the Gemini app and Whisk as <a href=\"https://one.google.com/about/ai-premium/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://one.google.com/about/ai-premium/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google One AI Premium subscribers</a>.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 宣布 Gemini Advanced 和 Whisk 现已支持 Veo 2 模型，用户可通过文本和图像提示生成视频，旨在增强创作可能性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 宣布 Gemini Advanced 和 Whisk 现已支持 Veo 2 模型，用户可通过文本和图像提示生成视频，旨在增强创作可能性。",
  "summary": "Google DeepMind 博客宣布，Gemini Advanced 用户现在可以使用 Veo 2 模型生成和分享视频。此功能将文本提示转换为动态视频。此外，Veo 2 还通过 Google Labs 实验项目 Whisk 提供，允许用户使用文本和图像提示来动画化图像。Veo 2 旨在生成具有电影写实感的高分辨率、详细视频，理解真实世界的物理和人类运动，以提供流畅的角色运动和逼真的场景。视频生成为 8 秒片段，分辨率为 720p，宽高比为 16:9。所有使用 Veo 2 生成的视频都标有数字水印 SynthID，表明内容由 AI 生成。Google 已经实施了诸如红队测试和 SynthID 水印之类的安全措施，以防止违反政策。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Veo 2：Gemini 和 Whisk 中的高质量视频生成。",
      "explanation": "该模型生成具有逼真的物理和运动的详细、高分辨率视频，从而增强了 Gemini 和 Whisk 平台内的创意表达。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Whisk Animate：让图像栩栩如生。",
      "explanation": "用户可以使用 Veo 2 将静态图像转换为动态的 8 秒视频，从而扩展创作可能性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "视频生成的安全保障。",
      "explanation": "Google 使用红队测试和 SynthID 水印来防止违反政策并表明内容由 AI 生成。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Veo 2 代表视频生成技术的飞跃，旨在创造具有电影级真实感的高分辨率精细视频。",
    "使用 Gemini 创建视频非常简单：只需描述您想创作的场景——无论是短篇故事、视觉概念还是特定场景——Gemini 就能将您的想法变为现实。",
    "Whisk Animate 让您能够利用 Veo 2 将图像转化为栩栩如生的 8 秒视频。"
